	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_002067_0001"><!--pb/@n='78r'--></pb>
<lb/><p rend="right">Monday morning</p>
<lb/><space dim="vertical" extent="2" unit="lines"/>
<lb/><p>My Dear<persName>Waller</persName></p>
<lb/><p>Could you show
<lb/>a gigantic human
<lb/>head - not an
<lb/>ugly one - with
<lb/>a lip ring in it
<lb/>to show at the
<lb/>theatre tonight.
<lb/>I shall see you 
<lb/>at the section of 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_002067_0002"><!--pb/@n='78v'--></pb>
<lb/>of geography today</p>
<lb/><p><persName><choice><abbr>D L</abbr><expan>David Livingstone</expan></choice></persName> is in <add place="above">the</add><add place="below">^</add> terrific
<lb/>labour pains of
<lb/>his mouse - <choice><sic>wont</sic><corr>won't</corr></choice>
<lb/>mention <persName>Bishop <choice><abbr>T.</abbr><expan>Tozer</expan></choice></persName>
<lb/>at all</p><!-- Bleedthrough from recto side evident HB 9/25/12 -->

